      <header className="relative z-30">
        <nav className="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-6 py-6 flex items-center justify-between">
          <div className="flex items-center gap-3">
            <div className="flex items-center justify-center w-12 h-12 rounded-2xl bg-gradient-to-br from-indigo-600 via-purple-600 to-blue-500 shadow-lg">
              <svg width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" aria-hidden>
                <path d="M4 12c0-4 4-8 8-8s8 4 8 8-4 8-8 8-8-4-8-8z" fill="white" opacity="0.06"/>
                <path d="M7 12c0-2.761 2.239-5 5-5" stroke="white" strokeWidth="1.4" strokeLinecap="round" strokeLinejoin="round"/>
                <path d="M12 7v10" stroke="white" strokeWidth="1.4" strokeLinecap="round" strokeLinejoin="round"/>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <div>
              <div className="text-lg font-semibold">IntegraIA</div>
              <div className="text-xs text-gray-500">Integração inteligente para empresas</div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div className="flex items-center gap-4">
            <a href="#servicos" className="hidden md:inline-block text-sm font-medium">Serviços</a>
            <a href="#cases" className="hidden md:inline-block text-sm font-medium">Casos</a>
            <a href="#contato" className="hidden md:inline-block text-sm font-medium">Contato</a>
            <a href="#contato" className="inline-flex items-center gap-2 rounded-full bg-gradient-to-r from-indigo-600 via-purple-600 to-blue-500 px-4 py-2 text-white text-sm shadow-md transform transition hover:scale-105">Solicitar Orçamento</a>
          </div>
        </nav>
      </header>

      <main className="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-6 pb-20">
        {/* HERO */}
        <section className="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center pt-12">
          <div>
            <h1 className="text-4xl sm:text-5xl font-extrabold leading-tight">IntegraIA — bots de Inteligência Artificial que atuam como time</h1>
            <p className="mt-6 text-lg text-gray-600 max-w-xl">Ajudamos empresas a automatizar atendimento, aumentar conversões e reduzir custos com soluções de bots inteligentes, treinados e integrados com sua operação usando Chatbase e outras plataformas líderes.</p>

            <div className="mt-8 flex gap-4">
              <a href="#contato" className="inline-flex items-center gap-3 rounded-lg bg-gray-900 px-5 py-3 text-white font-semibold shadow-lg transition hover:opacity-95">Fale conosco</a>
              <a href="#servicos" className="inline-flex items-center gap-3 rounded-lg border border-gray-200 px-5 py-3 text-sm font-medium">Nossos serviços</a>
            </div>

            <div className="mt-10 grid grid-cols-2 gap-4 max-w-md">
              <div className="bg-white/60 backdrop-blur-md rounded-2xl p-4 shadow-md">
                <div className="text-xs font-semibold text-gray-700">Economia</div>
                <div className="mt-2 text-xl font-bold">Redução de custos</div>
                <div className="mt-1 text-sm text-gray-600">Atendimento 24/7 e respostas rápidas que diminuem a necessidade de escala humana.</div>
              </div>
              <div className="bg-white/60 backdrop-blur-md rounded-2xl p-4 shadow-md">
                <div className="text-xs font-semibold text-gray-700">Crescimento</div>
                <div className="mt-2 text-xl font-bold">Aumento de conversões</div>
                <div className="mt-1 text-sm text-gray-600">Respostas orientadas por intenção e fluxos otimizados para conversão.</div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div className="relative">
            <div className="absolute -right-8 -top-8 w-80 h-80 rounded-3xl bg-gradient-to-br from-indigo-600 to-purple-600 opacity-20 blur-3xl transform rotate-12" />

            <div className="relative rounded-2xl bg-white shadow-2xl overflow-hidden border border-gray-100">
              <div className="p-6">
                <div className="flex items-center justify-between">
                  <div className="text-sm font-semibold">Conversa de demonstração</div>
                  <div className="text-xs text-gray-400">IntegraIA</div>
                </div>

